org.jetel.component.fileoperation

Class PathInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.component.fileoperation.PathInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Info

    public class PathInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements Info
    An implementation of Info used primarily for listing local files.

    File metadata are cached at the time the object is created, may be outdated at the time they are requested.
